    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "COLFAX, Wash, Feb. lit is\nstated here by George Garfield, one\nof the men who have charge of the\nSpokane & Inland roads interests\nin Whitman county, that 1000 men\nwill be brought to this place as\nsoon as camps are established.\nThey will be put to work on the\n62 miles of road which is to be\nbuilt from Colfax to a place near\nWaverly."
    }
